    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Technique achieved by applying paint using the digits of the hand rather than a brush. Examples range from prehistoric image-making, modern art-making techniques, and children's art.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
